---
title: Sesame Ground Pork Bowl with Garlic-Cauliflower Rice
description: There’s nothing like a cauliflower rice dish to make you feel a bit fancy at dinnertime. This colourful beauty celebrates tender-crisp veggies, sesame pork and the finishing touch of crisp of green onions. It’s unbeatable!

